OL,4,Ctwo 14-year-old girls
OL,6,FA man has been charged with the rape
OL,7,Fof two 14-year-old girls in Bolton.
OL,9,FGreater Manchester Police says it
OL,10,Freceived a report of a rape at a flat
OL,11,Fin the Middle Hulton area in the early
OL,12,Fhours of Sunday 7 December.
OL,14,FOfficers arrested Sultani Bakatash, a
OL,15,F28-year-old Afghan national, in
OL,16,Fconnection with the alleged incident.
OL,18,FHe has since been charged with two
OL,19,Fcounts of rape of a girl aged under
OL,20,F16, one count of sexual assault and
OL,21,Fone count of assault by penetration.
