OL,6,FBakatash, born March 21, 1997, has
OL,7,Fbeen remanded into custody. He is due
OL,8,Fto appear at Manchester and Salford
OL,9,FMagistrates Court on Tuesday 9
OL,10,FDecember.
OL,12,FA GMP spokesperson said the two girls
OL,13,Fare being supported by specialist
OL,14,Fteams as officers continue to
OL,15,Finvestigate the full circumstances of
OL,16,Fthe alleged incident.
