OL,6,FChief Superintendent Helen Critchley,
OL,7,FBolton district commander, said: "This
OL,8,Fis a deeply concerning report, and our
OL,9,Fpriority is supporting the two young
OL,10,Fgirls and their families at this
OL,11,Ftraumatic time.
OL,13,F"We have acted quickly since this was
OL,14,Freported to us in the last 48 hours,
OL,15,Fand we've been using all available
OL,16,Fresources to understand what has
OL,17,Fhappened and help this case progress
OL,18,Fthrough court.
