OL,6,F"We remain firmly committed to
OL,7,Fprotecting young girls in Bolton and
OL,8,Facross Greater Manchester and to help
OL,9,Fpeople feel safe in their
OL,10,Fneighbourhood.
OL,12,F"I ask that the public continue to
OL,13,Fsupport us while we do whatever is
OL,14,Fnecessary to support the girls and to
OL,15,Fget this case solved. As criminal
OL,16,Fproceedings are now active, I urge the
OL,17,Fpublic not to speculate so that the
OL,18,Flegal process can take its proper
OL,19,Fcourse and the dignity of the girls is
OL,20,Fmaintained."
